```
 Where err_log.txt is a file I created in the moodle/error/ folder. Permissions on the file are 0666 and the folder 0755. After creating the file, I purged caches and attempted to open a questionnaire. The redirect still happened. Nothing was written to the err_log.txt. Server phpinfo.php says that the following values are set: Directive Local Value Master Value error_log /error/err_log.txt error_log log_errors On On Questions: Has anyone encountered this before? Were you able to fix it, and if so, how? Does anyone in general have suggestions as to what to try next? Have I set up error logging correctly?

